{"tid":1220891,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"民陣請入，星期日改做”集會”得唔得，係咪好過”遊行”？","createTime":"2019-06-14T05:44:58.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-14T08:18:53.000Z","uid":244332,"like":4,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"4d739a5e15bacf5693547394300142281e370aa3","tid":1220891,"uid":244332,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T05:44:58.000Z","msg":"第一，上次行完，如果今次遊行唔夠上次多人會否有反效果？ 就算有上次咁多人，又係咪有好大作用先？<br />\n<br />\n第二，集會就算冇上次多人，都唔會有比較，而且集會塞埋一齊個感覺都會好多好多人。如果有一百萬人，合法集會既效果更加唔洗講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\nbtw, 希望你地唔好籌款，唔好俾位人入。如果今次唔夠多人，效果又冇用，好驚會分裂得仲勁過之前<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n結論：6/16見，點都要多人過上次<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c35e83a016adac91b7b62a88f1146c7d4de6f37c","tid":1220891,"uid":196924,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T05:46:11.000Z","msg":"唔行既話堅尼地城去到柴灣先勉強塞得入100萬"},{"pid":"15614f492e57091da3eac50683b613a0a85241fd","tid":1220891,"uid":244332,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T08:18:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}